{"tid":2183302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅稱韋德齊訪台將付出代價 在台捷克人反嗆「去死吧」","createTime":"2020-09-01T00:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T01:56:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b53e7a8ce22695d9483c89c104e0ab42d95c4ec7","tid":2183302,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:43:31.000Z","msg":"捷克參議院議長韋德齊日前率團訪台，卻被中國外交部長王毅批評是「公開挑釁」，揚言會讓韋德齊及背後的反華勢力付出「沉重代價」。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n在台北經營捷克餐酒館的捷克籍老闆皮哈（Karel Picha）則直言：「大部分捷克人應該會對他說『去死吧』。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n因此捷克人民只要聽到有任何一個共產國家威脅捷克，「我們就會恨得咬牙切齒」。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n然而大部分捷克人民也不會害怕被中國報復，尤其是捷克的經濟其實並不依賴中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3277575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3277575&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7jcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e483a5c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3277575&h=7611243b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3277575</a>"},{"pid":"c61296397d39d9ddc1b823578f079e9aefab3161","tid":2183302,"uid":7323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">去到邊都俾人追住來屌</span>"},{"pid":"3f6068603b9d116456b90bb9ed7eb1e9cb0bd880","tid":2183302,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:49:35.000Z","msg":"吳京去咗邊？戰狼去咗邊？"},{"pid":"790fef4571ee3a4722f08b239b40214074b2b6c7","tid":2183302,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:12:39.000Z","msg":"王毅對比pompeo訪歐結盟，真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a7095883e63352087ea292cd7bf9ca591adb07","tid":2183302,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T01:15:46.000Z","msg":"賤族賤種賤名：蝗蟻<br />\n<br />\n畜牲才會用